859
01:07:11,344 --> 01:07:13,364
So? What'd ya come up with?

860
01:07:13,488 --> 01:07:15,058
Got an evacuation plan?

861
01:07:18,964 --> 01:07:21,498
A... A... A bomb?!

862
01:07:21,938 --> 01:07:26,237
Yeah, we have water gel explosives we
use for construction at our storage site.

863
01:07:26,284 --> 01:07:27,798
