A start up frequency can hijack the
town's warning system pretty easily.

865
01:07:33,048 --> 01:07:36,892
So we can broadcast an evacuation warning
for the whole town right from school!

866
01:07:37,254 --> 01:07:39,386
Look, we're outside the disaster area here,

867
01:07:39,664 --> 01:07:42,080
so we'll just make an announcement
to evacuate to the school.

868
01:07:42,413 --> 01:07:45,118
It's... It's totally a crime.

869
01:07:45,184 --> 01:07:46,857
You'll be in charge of the broadcast, Saya.

870
01:07:46,892 --> 01:07:47,637
Why me?!

871
01:07:47,670 --> 01:07:49,172
You're in the broadcast club.

872
01:07:49,432 --> 01:07:51,192
And I'll be in charge of the explosives.

873
01:07:51,244 --> 01:07:53,062
While I go have a word with the mayor.

874
01:07:53,087 --> 01:07:53,447
Why?

875
01:07:53,524 --> 01:07:58,058
'Cause if the evacuation order's not coming
from town hall, then nobody's gonna go anywhere.

876
01:07:58,104 --> 01:08:01,029
But if I talk to the mayor, as
his daughter, I can convince him.

877
01:08:01,415 --> 01:08:02,744
It's the perfect plan.

878
01:08:04,552 --> 01:08:06,914
Fine, I don't really care one way or the other.

879
01:08:07,220 --> 01:08:09,062
This is just a theory of yours, right?

880
01:08:09,495 --> 01:08:11,557
Uh. Well...

881
01:08:11,710 --> 01:08:13,307
Theories can be based on reality!

882
01:08:13,366 --> 01:08:15,872
Like, do you know the story
of how Itomori Lake was formed?

883
01:08:16,104 --> 01:08:17,252
It's a crater!

884
01:08:17,394 --> 01:08:21,358
That means a meteor hit this area
at least once a thousand years ago!

885
01:08:21,610 --> 01:08:23,323
Right! That's why...

886
01:08:23,709 --> 01:08:25,312
Nice one, Teshi!

887
01:08:29,323 --> 01:08:31,323
Let's go evacuate the town!

888
01:08:35,403 --> 01:08:37,424
What on earth are you talking about?

889
01:08:39,537 --> 01:08:43,317
Like I said, we have to evacuate
everyone in town before tonight or else...

890
01:08:43,342 --> 01:08:44,649
Enough. Shut up!

891
01:08:50,392 --> 01:08:53,446
